  "special": {
    "title": "It's closer than you think! (no it isn't)",
    "description": "Fires a fixed sideways figure-eight. Effectively no ammo consumption and no normal reloads, with a fixed magazine of 1. Reduced damage and fire rate. Aiming down sights tightens the pattern but does not remove it."
  },
  "notes": "Drops in True Vault Hunter Mode and above. Needs at least 1 pistol round in reserves to fire. Fixed mag enables Zer0's 0ne Sh0t 0ne Kill every shot. Strong with Gaige: Cooking Up Trouble sustain, Close Enough ricochets, and safe Anarchy stacking (no accidental reload), but Discord cannot trigger. Dva variant has a 1-in-4 chance to add a second bullet. Can spawn without an accessory; elemental prefixes (or Rapid if non-elemental), no grip prefixes. Every 8th shot is perfectly accurate at the crossover; great on Loaders, weaker on small distant targets. Mag size to 0 makes it unusable; Neutral",
